set="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeff-Schroder-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>吉他手 Jeff Schroeder 宣布推出他的首张“冥想”个人专辑“Metanoia”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-smashing-pumpkins-atum-review-3438260">《粉碎南瓜》——“ATUM”评论：带有赞歌的夸张太空摇滚歌剧</a></strong></li></ul><p>Schroeder 和独立唱片公司 Clerestory AV 的 Instagram 帐户上分享的一篇帖子表示，《Metanoia》将“以氛围先锋<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-fripp">Fripp</a>和<a href="/artists/brian-eno">Eno</a>的精神呈现 72 分钟的冥想吉他作品”。</p><p>该专辑定于 8 月 23 日通过 Clerestory AV 发行，并将以限量版折叠双 LP（仅限 300 份）和磁带（仅限 100 份）形式发售。您可以<a href="https://www.clerestoryav.com/store/cav030" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订专辑</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9zfWMBRoYH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #