r_mercury_prize.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury_prize-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury_prize-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury_prize-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury_prize-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/english_teacher_mercury_prize-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">英语老师</a>向<em>NME</em>谈到了入围<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>、他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BEYONCE">碧昂丝</a>的“竞争”以及第二张专辑的进展。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">封面上的英语老师：来自英国吉他音乐中心的重要声音</a></strong></li></ul><p>利兹独立新贵<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">昨天（7 月 25 日星期四）获得了 Mercury 的认可</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785">前<em>NME</em>封面明星</a>的广受好评的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">“This Could Be Texas”</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">Ghetts</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party 等</a>唱片一起入围。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corinne-bailey-rae">科琳·贝利·雷 (Corinne Bailey Rae)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">贝丝·吉本斯 (Beth Gibbons)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">巴里不会游泳</a>等。</p><p> <em>NME</em>被问及提名的含义时，女主持人莉莉·方丹（Lily Fontaine）将其描述为“精神”，并将今年的提名人称为“迄今为止最好的一年。不仅是因为我们在上面！”</p><p>吉他手刘易斯·惠廷（Lewis Whiting）对“这可能是德克萨斯州的生活”的询问是关于2024年的生活，其目的是捕捉这个想法：“通常相距甚远，通常非常相似”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C92pA9Wo0-H/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 